	<br>
      <p>Adriana Barriga is an RPM Provider in the Dallas-Fort Worth area. She graduated from the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill in 2008 with a Bachelor of Arts in Speech and Hearing Sciences. Since returning to Fort Worth, Texas, she has been practicing RPM since 2012 with various students across the metroplex. She began her formal RPM training in July of 2014, completing the introductory course at HALO in Austin, Texas. In 2015, she was invited to complete the internship at HALO, training with Soma Mukhopadhyay. Adriana completed her internship in November 2016, and she is now a Certified RPM Provider. She continues to work with students and families across Dallas-Fort Worth.</p>
      
